\chapter{System Design and Implementation}\label{chapter:system-design}

Chapter~4 operationalises the five configurations at a level of detail sufficient for
independent re-implementation from the released artefact.

\section{System Components and Data Flow}\label{sec:sys:components}

Figure~\ref{fig:sys-components} shows the static component view. A run is initiated
