\paragraph{Reproducibility.}
Three commitments support reproducibility: deterministic sampling under
\texttt{seed=42}; explicit version pinning of model identifiers (full provider
snapshot strings) in the run metadata; and persistence of the full trace bundle
(rendered prompts, completions, parsed answers, diagnostics) so that the statistical
pipelines of Section~\ref{sec:meth:stats} can be regenerated from raw logs without
rerunning models. The prompt registry version hash is written to every run record,
making prompt content auditable independently of the run logs.
